Series was exactly what I expected! I loved the old cartoons and wanted my son to be able to experience them as well! Had an issue but it turned out to be my DVD player, not the product. I emailed the Seller and he was quick to respond and very helpful! Great buy!

I have been a Scooby Doo fan for over 20 years and thought this was very cute. I did not know this series was created so I had to purchase when I found it. This series centers around the gang as children (elementary) and solving cute kiddie cases. I have watched both series and thought they were awesome; very cute. The cases in the series are hard to figure out (which was very shocking) and my children absolutely loved it. My children are now huge Scooby Doo fans thanks to this series!! Great find, great price and I would order from the seller again.

A great set to get for the Scooby lover in your family. It is the gang in grade school and Scooby-Do is a pup. My daughter loves it and I would recommend it to anyone who is looking for a set of Scooby-Do mysteries.
I really like it I am so please with my order and my order came on time thank you so much I really appreciate
